</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_542" id="270r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Ritter <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Hanns<ex>en</ex></expan> von Waldenvells</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> Hanns, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von Ott Eybans
                                    <add><expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan></add>, wie dem gesagt sey,
                        daz er versagt oder in schulden gen uns süll sein, darauf ir im geleyts von
                        uns begert etc., das haben wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>. Und
                        wenn <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan> Ott Eyban
                        <expan>hiezwisch<ex>en</ex></expan> <app><note><q type="date">sand Niclas tag schierist</q>06.12.1422</note></app> zu uns gen
                                <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan>
<expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> wil, so sol er umb
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> willen zu und von uns für uns und die
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> on <expan>gev<ex>er</ex>de</expan>
                        drey tag geleyt <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>, alsdenn wellen wir sein rede
                                <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> hören. Denn wo wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> ii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Martini.</ab>
</div>
